      "rationale": "Four-level h-refinement study conducted on the non-cannulated construct model. Peak von Mises stress at screw-rod interface changed by 0.6% between fine (0.45 mm) and extra-fine (0.3 mm) meshes. Richardson extrapolation yields GCI of 1.3%, confirming discretization error is well controlled. Final production mesh uses fine discretization."
