      "rationale": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) satisfy both acceptance criteria. Maximum E/uval = 1.12 (yield force); maximum relative error = 2.0% (stiffness). Validation uncertainty uval computed per ASME V&V 10-2006 incorporating experimental repeatability and model input uncertainty."
    },
    {
