      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three primary endpoints specified in ASTM F1717 and referenced in FDA guidance for pedicle screw 510(k) submissions. These QoIs are directly relevant to the clinical COU and the regulatory decision."
