    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for a Medium model risk, Medium model influence, Medium decision consequence profile. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted on the basis that the tested condition represents the clinically relevant worst case and all quantitative acceptance criteria are satisfied with margin. Overall credibility is judged sufficient to support regulatory use of the FEA model for the stated COU.",
